Time travel + blue pants + lightning bolts coming out of forehead = ???

1987 called and demanded that I post a record of this game on Youtube so that future generations may learn.

This time around I found the music pretty boring so I used Ferrara's Hysteria Tune 3 remake instead. Sorry, purists. Oh, and sorry for using a trainer, too :D The game is hard enough that I don't think I would have made it to level 2 after all these years without practice. :)
